com.joliciel.talismane.fr.ftb.Phrase

  • Packages that use Phrase 
    Package Description
    com.joliciel.talismane.fr.ftb
    A package for reading the French Treebank in its native XML format, and writing the contents to a PostGreSQL database for ease of query and manipulation.
    com.joliciel.talismane.fr.ftb.search
    A package for searching the French Treebank using various patterns once it has been uploaded to a database.
